A post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit.

At the entrance, event staff scan registrations and hand out lanyards, while healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos.

Near the stage, a resume review table allows human resources teams to provide feedback on attendees' resumes while taking notes on tablets as students introduce themselves, presenting opportunities for professional development. Friends relax on the quad, discussing their positive interactions with company representatives and analyzing which recruiters appeared most enthusiastic. A data science company showcases a live dashboard displaying fair attendance and insights into event participation, while healthcare providers display community outreach photos. A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session, and workshops on networking etiquette are held in an adjoining classroom. Additionally, a post-event survey link flashes on monitors near the exit, enhancing attendee engagement, while event staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards at the entrance.
